# [Project Name]
<!-- One-line description: what this project does and why it exists -->
[e.g., REST API for duty-free sales management — Java 21 / Spring Boot 3 / AWS ECS]

## Communication Policy
- Respond in **Japanese** when the user writes in Japanese.
- All source code, variable names, and code comments must be written in **English**.

## Tech Stack
- **Language / Runtime**: [Java 21 / TypeScript 5 / Python 3.12]
- **Framework**: [Spring Boot 3 / Next.js 15 / FastAPI]
- **Build / Package manager**: [Gradle / pnpm / uv]
- **Database**: [PostgreSQL / MySQL 8 / DynamoDB]
- **Infrastructure**: [AWS ECS Fargate / Docker / Terraform]

## Essential Commands
```bash
[dev]          # Start dev server / local run
[test-single]  # Run a single test  e.g. ./gradlew test --tests "FooTest"
[test-all]     # Run full test suite e.g. ./gradlew test
[lint]         # Lint + static analysis
[build]        # Production build (skip tests)
[deploy]       # Deploy to staging  (if applicable)
```

## Structure
```
src/
  [domain|feature]/   # Domain / feature modules
  [api|routes]/       # Controllers / entry points
  [service|usecase]/  # Business logic
  [repository|dao]/   # Data access layer
  [model|entity]/     # Data models
  [config]/           # Configuration
tests/                # Mirrors src/
docs/                 # Architecture decisions, guides
infra/                # IaC (CDK / Terraform)
```

## Detailed Rules
<!-- Keep this file lean. Detailed conventions live in .claude/rules/ -->
- Code style & naming:  `.claude/rules/code-style.md`
- Architecture patterns: `.claude/rules/architecture.md`
- Testing strategy:      `.claude/rules/testing.md`
- Security guidelines:   `.claude/rules/security.md`  ← read before touching auth/infra

## Non-Negotiable Constraints
<!-- Critical safety rules are ALSO enforced via .claude/settings.json deny rules.
     Listed here only as human-readable documentation. -->
- Never commit `.env` or any `.env.*` file
- Never force-push to `main` / `develop`
- Never read or log secrets / credentials
- Always run `[lint] && [test-all]` before committing

## Landmines & Gotchas
<!-- Format: WHEN [condition] → DO / NEVER [action]
     Add entries here whenever Claude makes the same mistake twice. -->
- When editing `[migration files]` → run `[migration-cmd]` before starting
- `[auto-generated file]` is generated by `[generation-cmd]` — never edit directly
- When touching `[critical-module]` → read `docs/[module-guide].md` first

## Key Documentation
- Architecture overview: `docs/architecture.md`
- API specification:     `docs/api-spec.md`
- Deployment guide:      `docs/deploy.md`
- Decision records:      `docs/adr/`
